---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - CC3PO">
	<Header />
	
	<style>
		.page-hero {
			min-height: 50vh;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			padding: 120px 24px 60px;
		}
		.page-hero-inner {
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.page-hero-inner h1 {
			font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
			font-weight: 800;
			line-height: 1.1;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, #a78bfa 60%, #00d2ff 100%);
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-clip: text;
		}
		.page-hero-inner p {
			font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
			color: #a1a1aa;
			max-width: 640px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		.section {
			padding: 80px 24px;
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		.section-dark {
			background: var(--card);
		}
		.section-header {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 48px;
		}
		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
			font-weight: 700;
			margin-bottom: 12px;
		}
		.section-header p {
			color: #a1a1aa;
			font-size: 16px;
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		.story-content {
			max-width: 720px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		.story-content p {
			font-size: 16px;
			line-height: 1.8;
			color: #a1a1aa;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}
		.story-content strong {
			color: #fff;
		}
		.values-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
			gap: 24px;
		}
		.value-card {
			background: linear-gradient(145deg, #141418, #0f0f11);
			border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
			border-radius: 20px;
			padding: 36px;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}
		.value-card:hover {
			border-color: rgba(107, 53, 255, 0.3);
			transform: translateY(-4px);
		}
		.value-icon {
			font-size: 36px;
			margin-bottom: 16px;
		}
		.value-card h3 {
			font-size: 20px;
			margin-bottom: 12px;
		}
		.value-card p {
			color: #a1a1aa;
			font-size: 14px;
			line-height: 1.7;
		}
		.team-card {
			background: linear-gradient(145deg, #141418, #0f0f11);
			border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
			border-radius: 20px;
			padding: 48px;
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.team-avatar {
			width: 96px;
			height: 96px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: var(--grad);
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			font-size: 36px;
			font-weight: 800;
			margin: 0 auto 20px;
		}
		.team-card h3 {
			font-size: 24px;
			margin-bottom: 6px;
		}
		.team-title {
			color: var(--accent);
			font-size: 14px;
			margin-bottom: 16px;
		}
		.team-card p {
			color: #a1a1aa;
			font-size: 15px;
			line-height: 1.7;
		}
		.team-links {
			display: flex;
			gap: 16px;
			justify-content: center;
			margin-top: 20px;
		}
		.team-links a {
			color: var(--primary);
			font-size: 14px;
			font-weight: 600;
		}
		.stats-row {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
			gap: 24px;
			margin-top: 48px;
		}
		.about-stat {
			text-align: center;
			padding: 24px;
			background: rgba(107, 53, 255, 0.06);
			border-radius: 16px;
			border: 1px solid rgba(107, 53, 255, 0.12);
		}
		.about-stat-number {
			font-size: 36px;
			font-weight: 800;
			background: var(--grad);
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-clip: text;
			margin-bottom: 4px;
		}
		.about-stat-label {
			font-size: 13px;
			color: #a1a1aa;
		}
		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.page-hero {
				padding: 100px 16px 40px;
			}
			.section {
				padding: 60px 16px;
			}
		}
	</style>
	
	<main>
		<section class="page-hero">
			<div class="page-hero-inner">
				<span class="hero-badge">About Us</span>
				<h1>Building the Future of Dental IT</h1>
				<p>CC3PO stands for Client-Centered 3X Productivity Optimization. We combine AI agents with managed IT to help dental practices thrive.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>CC3PO started from a simple observation: <strong>dental practices are drowning in manual work</strong>. Front desks juggle scheduling, billing, insurance verification, and patient communications while the practice management software barely scratches the surface of what's possible.</p>
					<p>We built the <strong>AI Agent Village</strong> — Hermes, Atlas, and Prometheus — to do the work humans shouldn't have to. Each agent specializes in a domain: lead generation, data analytics, and operational automation. Together, they create a system that runs 24/7, continuously improving.</p>
					<p>Combined with our <strong>HIPAA-compliant managed IT services</strong>, we give dental practices a complete technology partner. From cybersecurity to cloud infrastructure to AI automation, everything is designed for one outcome: <strong>3X productivity without adding headcount</strong>.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="stats-row">
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="about-stat-number">3X</div>
						<div class="about-stat-label">Average Productivity Gain</div>
					</div>
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="about-stat-number">50+</div>
						<div class="about-stat-label">Organizations Served</div>
					</div>
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="about-stat-number">99.9%</div>
						<div class="about-stat-label">Agent Uptime</div>
					</div>
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="about-stat-number">90</div>
						<div class="about-stat-label">Days to Impact</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<section class="section-dark">
			<div class="section" style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="section-header">
						<h2>Our Values</h2>
					</div>
					
					<div class="values-grid">
						<div class="value-card">
							<div class="value-icon">&#x1F3AF;</div>
							<h3>Client-Centered</h3>
							<p>Every decision starts with the client. We measure success by the outcomes we deliver, not the hours we bill.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="value-card">
							<div class="value-icon">&#x26A1;</div>
							<h3>Systems Over People</h3>
							<p>We build systems that work regardless of who's at the desk. Consistency comes from process, not from heroics.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="value-card">
							<div class="value-icon">&#x1F4C8;</div>
							<h3>Compound Growth</h3>
							<p>Small improvements that compound over time beat one-time fixes. We optimize for trajectory, not snapshots.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="value-card">
							<div class="value-icon">&#x1F50D;</div>
							<h3>Radical Transparency</h3>
							<p>You see everything we see. Real-time dashboards, open reporting, and no black boxes. Trust is built through visibility.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Leadership</h2>
				</div>
				
				<div class="team-card">
					<div class="team-avatar">CC</div>
					<h3>Carlos Cabrales</h3>
					<p class="team-title">Founder & CEO</p>
					<p>Operations strategist turned AI infrastructure builder. Carlos has spent his career helping organizations eliminate inefficiency and scale through technology. He founded CC3PO to bring enterprise-grade automation to dental practices.</p>
					<div class="team-links">
						<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/carloscabrales" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn &rarr;</a>
						<a href="mailto:carlos@cc3po.com">Email &rarr;</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	
	<Footer />
</Layout>
